description:
We are the EARLY ADOPTER$.

The 50 first allocated awards are entitled to a whitelist spot for the EARLY ADOPTER$ Genesis NFT launch.

You can not have two or more whitelist spots for the same Metamask address. One Metamask address is entitled to a maximum of one whitelist spot. If you got awarded the first award in December, this one is not for you, you are already on the list.
